title: Molly en Wors - Die Movie 2013 Afrikaans DVDRip
description:
Molly and Wors have been together for 26 years, with two children Vaatjie and Shardonay. When Wors finally wins Salesman of the Year from his workplace, F1 Fitment Center, he also wins an overseas trip to Amsterdam.

His wife was supposed to go with, but circumstance led to him flying to the European country his own, leaving a fuming Molly behind. Wors is completely unaware of what is brewing at home, which could mean the end of a long happy marriage.


Cast:
    Lizz Meiring, Willie Esterhuizen , Gerhard Odendaal, Carien Botha, Marga van Rooy, Ben Kruger, Marcel van Heerden, Alvin Bruinders, Karen Wessels, Lelia Etsebeth, Joey Rasdien
Director:
    Willie Esterhuizen, Pieter Esterhuizen
Time:
    115 minutes
Genre:
    Comedy
